file.name: defn-with-query-params.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: "Definition with warning (missing version)."
  version: "0.1"
servers:
  - url: http://localhost:@@@PORT@@@/
paths:
  /content-json:
    get:
      parameters:
        - name: param
          in: query
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Tag'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK

components:
  schemas:
    Tag:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
          format: int64
        name:
          type: string
